Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ following \First Look-Your updates are overdue\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' occurs

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that reach \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ stage out of all manuscripts
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases where '' does not happen

Name: Number of times \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ is preceded by \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ that lead to \Manuscript Export Succeeded\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in relation to \SW-Reviewer Agreed\
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences after \First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ occurrences per year
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'group_by': 'time:timestamp'}

Name: Percentage of manuscripts that reach \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ without \SW-Reviewer No Response\
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases where 'SW-Reviewer No Response' does not happen

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ as the final activity in a manuscript's review process
Metric: Frequency of activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' for cases where activity 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ followed by any activity related to manuscript acceptance
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all 'RW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ preceded by \SW-EIC Major Revision\
Metric: Number of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision' occurs

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in manuscripts that underwent \SW–Major Revision due in 1 week\
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'metric_condition': '> 0', 'aggregation': 'percentage', 'filter': "activity == 'SW–Major Revision due in 1 week'"}

Name: Frequency of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in manuscripts with more than one \Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1\
Metric: the sum of the function base > 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Percentage of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ in relation to all activities performed by the SYSTEM performer
Metric: Percentage of 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch' out of all cases

Name: Number of \Awaiting Assignment to Batch\ for manuscripts that received \SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit\ decision
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'count': "activity == 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'", 'aggregation': 'total', 'filter': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'"}
